514
00:39:27.420 --> 00:39:29.910
and pray

515
00:39:30.080 --> 00:39:32.630
to be only yours

516
00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:36.720
I pray to be only yours

517
00:39:36.880 --> 00:39:38.620
I know now

518
00:39:39.050 --> 00:39:43.600
you're my only hope.

519
00:39:50.730 --> 00:39:54.150
Sing to me the song

520
00:39:54.770 --> 00:39:57.400
of the stars

521
00:40:00.150 --> 00:40:03.320
of your galaxy dancing

522
00:40:03.490 --> 00:40:07.490
and laughing and laughing again

523
00:40:09.120 --> 00:40:12.540
When it feels like my dreams

524
00:40:12.710 --> 00:40:15.460
are so far

525
00:40:18.090 --> 00:40:21.340
sing to me of the plans

526
00:40:21.510 --> 00:40:25.260
that you have for me over again

527
00:40:25.880 --> 00:40:27.680
So I lay

528
00:40:27.850 --> 00:40:32.390
my head back down

529
00:40:34.810 --> 00:40:38.810
and I lift my hands

530
00:40:38.980 --> 00:40:41.390
and pray

531
00:40:41.650 --> 00:40:44.190
to be only yours

532
00:40:48.570 --> 00:40:50.230
I know now

533
00:40:50.410 --> 00:40:55.750
you're my only hope

534
00:40:58.580 --> 00:41:01.950
I give you my destiny

