548
00:42:32.080 --> 00:42:33.030
Bravo!

549
00:42:38.840 --> 00:42:40.970
That was great.

550
00:42:46.300 --> 00:42:47.760
- Hi, kids.
- Hi.

551
00:42:48.310 --> 00:42:51.560
